  <entry>
    <title>对汇编的小理解</title>
    <link href="https://tsuppari404.github.io/2020/11/04/%E5%AF%B9%E6%B1%87%E7%BC%96%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%8F%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3/"/>
    <id>https://tsuppari404.github.io/2020/11/04/%E5%AF%B9%E6%B1%87%E7%BC%96%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%8F%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3/</id>
    <published>2020-11-04T14:15:15.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-11-06T06:03:51.266Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="/images/2020110401.jpg"></p><h4 id="用c-的方式来理解"><a href="#用c-的方式来理解" class="headerlink" title="用c++的方式来理解"></a>用c++的方式来理解</h4><p>mov ax,001AH -&gt; ax=001A (H表示16进制，001A是一位16进制数)<br>add ax,85H -&gt; ax+=85<br>add ax,bx -&gt; ax+=bx</p><h3 id="进行数据传送或运算的时候，指令的两个操作对象的位数应当是一致的，以下为错误指令"><a href="#进行数据传送或运算的时候，指令的两个操作对象的位数应当是一致的，以下为错误指令" class="headerlink" title="进行数据传送或运算的时候，指令的两个操作对象的位数应当是一致的，以下为错误指令"></a>进行数据传送或运算的时候，指令的两个操作对象的位数应当是一致的，以下为错误指令</h3><p>mov ax,bl (bl为8位寄存器，ax为16位寄存器)<br>mov al,20000 (al为8位寄存器，数据最大为2^8=256，0-255，而ax为16位寄存器，数据最大为2^16=65536,0-65535，均为十进制)<br>mov al,100H (100H已超出，16进制中1位相当于2进制中4位)</p><p>注意al和ah是构成ax的两个8位寄存器，我第一次看的时候没注意蒙了半天<br><img src="/images/2020110402.jpg"></p><p>之前第一张图的代码用C++理解，代码如下(因为我对C++更熟悉)</p><ol><li>ax=001AH;</li><li>bx=0026H;</li><li>al+=bl;<h3 id="以下省略…推荐在草稿纸上自行演示"><a href="#以下省略…推荐在草稿纸上自行演示" class="headerlink" title="以下省略…推荐在草稿纸上自行演示"></a>以下省略…推荐在草稿纸上自行演示</h3>计算机应用课上自己打的代码…因为实在是…懂得都懂，输入两个十六进制数，输出它们相加的结果(注意是大写字母)<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#include &lt;iostream&gt;</span><br><span class="line">#include &lt;cstring&gt;</span><br><span class="line">#include &lt;cstdio&gt;</span><br><span class="line">using namespace std;</span><br><span class="line">int main()</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">char a[500],b[500];</span><br><span class="line">int a1[500],b1[500],al,bl,i,max1,ans[500];</span><br><span class="line">cin&gt;&gt;a&gt;&gt;b;</span><br><span class="line">al&#x3D;strlen(a);</span><br><span class="line">bl&#x3D;strlen(b);</span><br><span class="line">for(i&#x3D;al;i&gt;&#x3D;1;i--)a[i]&#x3D;a[i-1];</span><br><span class="line">for(i&#x3D;bl;i&gt;&#x3D;1;i--)b[i]&#x3D;b[i-1];</span><br><span class="line">max1&#x3D;max(al,bl);</span><br><span class="line">for(i&#x3D;1;i&lt;&#x3D;max1+1;i++)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">a1[i]&#x3D;0;</span><br><span class="line">b1[i]&#x3D;0;</span><br><span class="line">ans[i]&#x3D;0;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">for(i&#x3D;al;i&gt;&#x3D;1;i--)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">if(a[i]&gt;&#x3D;&#39;0&#39;&amp;&amp;a[i]&lt;&#x3D;&#39;9&#39;)a1[al-i+1]&#x3D;int(a[i])-int(&#39;0&#39;);</span><br><span class="line">if(a[i]&gt;&#x3D;&#39;A&#39;&amp;&amp;a[i]&lt;&#x3D;&#39;F&#39;)a1[al-i+1]&#x3D;int(a[i])-55;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">for(i&#x3D;bl;i&gt;&#x3D;1;i--)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">if(b[i]&gt;&#x3D;&#39;0&#39;&amp;&amp;b[i]&lt;&#x3D;&#39;9&#39;)b1[bl-i+1]&#x3D;int(b[i])-int(&#39;0&#39;);</span><br><span class="line">if(b[i]&gt;&#x3D;&#39;A&#39;&amp;&amp;b[i]&lt;&#x3D;&#39;F&#39;)b1[bl-i+1]&#x3D;int(b[i])-55;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;for(i&#x3D;1;i&lt;&#x3D;al;i++)cout&lt;&lt;a1[i]&lt;&lt;&quot; &quot;;</span><br><span class="line">for(i&#x3D;1;i&lt;&#x3D;max1;i++)ans[i]&#x3D;a1[i]+b1[i];</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;for(i&#x3D;1;i&lt;&#x3D;max1;i++)cout&lt;&lt;ans[i]&lt;&lt;&quot; &quot;;</span><br><span class="line">int h,j;</span><br><span class="line">for(i&#x3D;1;i&lt;&#x3D;max1;i++)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">h&#x3D;0;</span><br><span class="line">if(ans[i]&gt;&#x3D;16)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">h&#x3D;ans[i]&#x2F;16;</span><br><span class="line">ans[i]%&#x3D;16;</span><br><span class="line">ans[i+1]+&#x3D;h;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">if(ans[max1+1]!&#x3D;0)max1++;</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;for(i&#x3D;al;i&gt;&#x3D;1;i--)cout&lt;&lt;a1[i]&lt;&lt;&quot; &quot;;</span><br><span class="line">for(i&#x3D;max1;i&gt;&#x3D;1;i--)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">if(ans[i]&gt;&#x3D;0&amp;&amp;ans[i]&lt;&#x3D;9)cout&lt;&lt;ans[i];</span><br><span class="line">else cout&lt;&lt;char(ans[i]+55);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">return 0;</span><br><span class="line">&#125; </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><p>输入样例：<br>4E20<br>406<br>输出样例:<br>5226</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/images/2020110401.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
